        <body>
            
            <div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><g type="pc"/> śubham astu supa
                </ab>
                <p>
                    śrīmaN mahā-maṇṭalēśvaran rājādirāja rāja paramēśvara śrī vīra pratāpa śrī vīra śrī vēṅkaṭapati deva mahārāyar pritivi rājyam paṇṇi Aruḷā niṉṟa
                    <lb n="2"/>śāli-vāhana-śa<choice><sic>kh</sic><corr>k</corr></choice>āptam 1509 n mēl cellā niṉṟa sarvaśitti samvaśśarattu vaiśākha nāyaṟṟu pūrva pakṣattu yintu vasaramum pañcamiyum peṟṟa has<unclear>ta</unclear> nakṣattirattu nāḷ ceyaṅ ko
                    <lb n="3"/>ṇṭa cōḻa maṇṭalattu cantirakiri rājyam Ūṟṟuk kāṭṭuk kōṭṭattu viṟpēṭu nāṭṭil nakaram kāñcipuram viṣṇu stānattil tiru vekā nayinārkōyil śrī paṇṭārat
                    <lb n="4" break="no"/>tārum śrī kāriyam śrīmat vēta māṟka pratiṣṭāpaṉācārya Ubaiya vētāntācāryarāna Eṭṭūr tirumalai kumāra tāttācāryar Ayyan sannati Aḻakiya ciṅkarum ṣaṭa maruṣaṇa kōtrattu
                    <lb n="5"/>Āpastampa <gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> tāttācāryar tirumalai kumpakōṇam tāttācariyar Ayyā vayyaṅkār
                    <lb n="6"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> tirumā <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> yitta māka śopakṣaya taṟma śāsanam paṇṇi kuṭuttap paṭi
                    <lb n="7"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> vem perumāṉ <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> ṅkamāka Itukku mēṟku perumāḷ Eḻun taruḷum
                    <lb n="8"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> terutā tiru <gap reason="lost" quantity="16" unit="character"/> kaḷum maraṅkaḷum kiṇaṟukaḷum Uḷpaṭa Upakṣaya māka ni
                    <lb n="9"/>caṟcayitta <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> Aḻa <gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> Uḷḷa tellām maraṅkaḷ kiṇaṟukaḷ tiru ntavaṉam Uḷpaṭa <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> Upakṣaya māka cātanam paṇṇi kuṭuttōm Inta nilaṅkaḷ Uḷḷa tellām
                    <lb n="10"/>Aṣṭa bhoka tēca cuvāmiyaṅkaḷum putra pavutra pāramparai yāka Ācantrārtta māka tāna <gap reason="lost" quantity="7" unit="character"/> yaṅkaḷukkum yōkya māka Aṉupavittuk koḷḷak kaṭavarākavum Inta nilam Ellām Iv
                    <lb n="11"/>vemperumāṉ kōṭait tiru nāḷ koṇṭaruḷa poliyūṭṭu taṟma śāsanam paṇṇik kuṭukkayil In nilaṅkaḷ Ellām tiruk kōyililē kai koṇṭu Iv ve<unclear>m peru</unclear>māṉ kōṭait tiru nā
                    <lb n="12"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="31" unit="character"/> paṅkuṉi māsam puṇar pū <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> naṭattum piṟakāram ṉāḷ Oṉṟukku cuvāmi Eḻuntaruḷi cātti yaruḷa cantaṇam
                    <lb n="13"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> vilai <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ṣa perumāḷ kōyil pēril paṭi <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> Appam ka tōcai tūṇippatakku māmpaḻam puka vāḻaippaḻam puka veccamutu kaṃ
                    <lb n="14"/>Ilai yamutu 7 Alaṅkāra tiru mañcaṉam Uḷḷa kaṭṭaḷai Inta piṟakāram Āṟu ṉāḷum tiruk kōyililē naṭattak kaṭavōmākavum
                    <lb n="15"/>Amutu ceytaruḷiṉa ciṟappukku <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> viṭṭavaṉ viḻu <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> nālat toṉṟum Āḻvā <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> niṟuvākam ṉālukkum muṉṉāḷ tiruvaṭi kōyil paṭi poliyūṭṭu piṟa
                    <lb n="16"/>kāra <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> kuṭuttu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ṉiyōkam paṇṇivikka kaṭavōmākavum yippaṭi cammatittu kōṭait tiru ṉāḷ poliyūṭṭu nimattamāka Upakṣaya taṟma
                    <lb n="17"/>śāsanam paṇṇi kuṭuttōm tiruma <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> Ayyaṅkār Ayyan Avarkaḷukku tiruvekā nayiṉār kōyil śrī paṇṭārattārum śrī kāriyam ceyyum Aḻakiya ciṅkarum me<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>vai
                    <lb n="18"/>tiruc cittiṟa kūṭap paṭṭar coṉṉa vaṇṇam Eḻuttu ciṅkap pirāṉ paṭṭar nayiṉār <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>
                    19 <gap reason="lost" quantity="21" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="20"/>Āḻvār <gap reason="lost" quantity="20" unit="character"/>
                </p>
